---
title: Duck with Orange Sauce and Gremolata with mash and roasted carrots
description: Gremolata is a sauce of Italian origin made of chopped parsley and citrus zest. Our version contains a hint of orange, to complement the richness of the duck.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R13_W51_IE_IEXSD29406-6_MAIN_high-3ffe5c84.jpg
